snippet.title: Emma Frost OFFICIAL Trailer Full HD - Amber Heard, Margot Robbie, Scarlet Johansson Fan Concept
snippet.description:
Emma Frost is a little girl who is being bullied by her classmates and in her teenage years being harassed by her own father. Her life changes forever when she decides to take her life on her own hands but despite all her efforts one thing remains constant: she is a freak, a weirdo, a mutant. The only option she has, is to live like this, and never appear weak to anyone. Witness, the origins of thr X-Men villain Emma Frost and how she got where she is now. Emma Frost played by Scarlet Johansson, Amber Heard and Margot Robbie, all of whom play this iconic character in different times of her life.
_______________________________________
